g src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/64114300_1517533967.jpg" alt="222.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0em; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/72291600_1517533967.png" alt="图片-公众号-标题-女导师-导师故事.png"/></p><p><br/></p><section style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; color: inherit;"><section style="margin-top: 0.2em; padding-right: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(144, 21, 13); font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(247, 170, 165); border-top-color: rgb(247, 170, 165); border-right-color: rgb(247, 170, 165); border-left-color: rgb(247, 170, 165); box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-align: justify; max-width: 100%; line-height: 20.3636px;">用生命点燃他人灵魂之火的导师</span></strong></span></section><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 1em; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1; color: rgb(144, 21, 13); border-color: rgb(247, 170, 165);"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 13px;">晚 妆</span></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/78657200_1517533967.png" alt="图片-公众号-序号1.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0em; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70); font-size: 15px;"><strong><span style="max-width: 100%;">她是全球知名身心灵导师，</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70); font-size: 15px;"><strong>被称为“世界级心灵导航者”</strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(144, 21, 13);"></span></strong><strong><span style="color: rgb(144, 21, 13);"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">她是英国ASHACentre基金会女性成员之一，</span><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">是240位“全球最具影响力和启发性的成功女性”之一。</span><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">她的著作《对生命说是》，是全球500强企业团购第一名的励志书。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">她从29岁开始修行，在印度静心中心一住30年，之后又用了12年的时间在世界各地开设线下课程和线下工作坊。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">现在，她已经71岁了，却还是像17岁那样，时刻满怀热忱，内在平静喜悦。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0em; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;"><iframe class="video_iframe wx_video_iframe" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" width="558" height="419" src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/video_tmpl&vid=g0127o03ll5"></iframe></p><p style="margin-top: 0em; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px;">（点击上方视频，查看完整采访视频）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0em; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">华语世界首席身心灵作家张德芬曾赞其为：“她的状态是每个人都想学习的，虽然70多岁了，但是精力充沛，笑容可掬。在和她接触的过程中，觉得她最大的特点就是包容接纳，而且充满慈悲。</span><br/></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">她的智慧是令人艳慕的，每个人的问题，她只要看一眼，就可以知道症结所在，而且立刻以非常明快的手法对症下药。能上老师的课，真的是一件很幸运的事情。”</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">她就是奥南朵(Anando)。</span><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70);"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">一个用自己的生命点亮灵魂智慧，带领学员走向幸福的心灵导师。</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">而她个人的故事，不可谓传奇。</span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/89260200_1517533967.com/mmbiz_jpg/w2ktexcvd9ok8eiabpkvt8jhjdnfab2icih8sdpmpv0w5uqvfribpe5kjzk0v3uc5hspddhrefy6kxgpst9dvrgua/0" width="100%" height="auto" title="" alt="" style="white-space: normal; border: 1px solid rgb(220, 220, 221); border-radius: 0px; padding: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 6px;"/></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/95674400_1517533967.png" alt="图片-公众号-序号2.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0em; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);"><strong>从万众瞩目到一无所有，</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);"><strong>她经历了人生中最黑暗的时期</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">奥南朵出生在英国一个中产阶级家庭，物质条件相当优渥。所以，她从小就住在舒适的大房子里，读的是昂贵的私立学校，周围邻居也都是有钱人。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">而且她从小就容貌出众，还曾在数千名女孩中脱颖而出，被导演看中，在一部专业剧作中和当时出名的演员一起演出。</span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/3275100_1517533968.com/mmbiz/23esimufmd1tbkxcvmkq1ibhcm0dv5lsi7ebiurescii7kdamcicldtyfec9fybic7ymphiv2rte2quieirlu6acg/640" width="100%" height="auto" title="" alt="" style="white-space: normal; border: 1px solid rgb(220, 220, 221); border-radius: 0px; padding: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 6px;"/></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;">那段时间，她完全沉醉在了美妙的时光、美丽的憧憬，以及一定程度的名声之中。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">直到她的父亲因为事业破产而自杀，这种美好才被彻底打碎。她失去了父亲，也失去了自己的小马、自己的大房子、自己的所有资产，和妈妈一起搬进了出租房里。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">幸而，因为她一直成绩优异，有学校的奖学金作为支撑，得以留在原本的学校继续读书。但是，她和之前所有的朋友都断绝了来往，也不再像之前那样开朗。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">奥南朵后来回忆说：“那段时间，我经历了好几年的黑暗时期，为了驱散羞愧和自卑的阴影，我花了很长时间。”</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">但也正是那个时候的创伤，才最终引领她走入身心灵，更进一步地探索自己。</span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/9210500_1517533968.com/mmbiz_jpg/w2ktexcvd9ok8eiabpkvt8jhjdnfab2icihe5m9fpods8xlud5lfa6icqgckm6xd7bdyouwyhgfh0lqicrkuzgxtua/0" width="100%" height="auto" title="" alt="" style="white-space: normal; border: 1px solid rgb(220, 220, 221); border-radius: 0px; padding: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 6px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/15550500_1517533968.png" alt="图片-公众号-序号3.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0em; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70); font-size: 15px;"><strong>从自卑恐惧到绽放光芒，</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70); font-size: 15px;"><strong>她用舞蹈拯救了自己的灵魂</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(144, 21, 13);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></strong></span><br/><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">奥南朵就读的私立学校非常特殊，是一所几乎被隔离起来的女校，主要目的就是把女孩子训练成优秀的家庭主妇。</span><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">她是第一个考上大学法学系的。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">毫无疑问，在大学里，一个又容貌出众又成绩优异的少女会有多么受欢迎。那时候，有无数的男人苦苦追求，但是奥南朵却一个都没有答应。</span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/21088500_1517533968.com/mmbiz/p7p0t0l0bqxo8587vuetavvt0ich9zcxziajrgqkzs7v9ybecdaczdergwrt32ic2czn5scbubr4czwxsz3wboma/640" width="100%" height="auto" title="" alt="" style="white-space: normal; border: 1px solid rgb(220, 220, 221); border-radius: 0px; padding: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 6px;"/></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px;">（奥南朵和赖佩霞）</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">因为她的内心始终被深深的自卑感和不安全感包围着，不能理解他们怎么会爱上自己，也害怕自己会被抛弃。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">直到有一天，她发现了玛莎·葛兰姆舞蹈，第一次获得了超越头脑的体验，并且从安全感的匮乏中解放出来。于是，在通过执业律师考试，成为一名执业律师和法律顾问之后，她就立刻前往伦敦学习舞蹈。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">在那里，学习舞蹈的都是一些自小接受芭蕾舞训练的年轻少女，只有她一个二十多岁的学生。但是她毫不在意，甚至深感幸运。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70);"><strong><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">因为她觉得自己终于来到了另一个世界，得到了更多的灵性时刻。</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">也是在那时候，她遇到了自己的丈夫。</span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/47307800_1517533968.com/mmbiz_jpg/kf10ne2xwqniicd6gqtsuiniawl2gayicstfmdl6zky0dw5uiehqzfhig6fdh0niabtkcbab8yy4yiaymnivibyuoogq/0" width="100%" height="auto" title="" alt="" style="white-space: normal; border: 1px solid rgb(220, 220, 221); border-radius: 0px; padding: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 6px;"/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/52280700_1517533968.png" alt="图片-公众号-序号4.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0em; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70); font-size: 15px;"><strong><span style="max-width: 100%;">从拥有一切到放弃所有，</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70); font-size: 15px;"><strong><span style="max-width: 100%;">她一直在寻找生命的本质</span></strong></span><br/></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">奥南朵的丈夫约翰是一个艰苦的艺术家，为了生计，她离开舞蹈界，开始在一家报刊业做销售广告的工作，并很快成为了哈玛克出版旗下的商业杂志的助理出版人，负责《今日管理》《市场交易》《会计师时代》等，还身兼招聘部门的总经理。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">那个时候，妇女平等机会议案刚被议会通过，二十多岁就成为杰出的律师和商业杂志发行人的奥南朵受到了媒体的报道，并迅速走红，被誉为商业界成功女性。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">但是，越是成功，越是赚很多钱，奥南朵的压力就越大，越是没有安全感。她不知道人们什么时候就会发现自己并没有那么完美。更糟糕的是，她不敢把这些事告诉丈夫，因为他仍然很落魄。</span><br/></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">她和丈夫的距离越来越远，她的状态也越来越糟糕，甚至想到了自杀。她说：我每个早上都在想：我干吗要起床？</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70);"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">她拥有了外在的一切资源，内心却忽然找不到活着的意义了。</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">最终，她选择了离开丈夫和工作，独自来到一个小乡村，和一群年老的独居妇女学习编织。她设计的一双袜子还登上了当时的《时尚杂志》。</span><br/></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">她还开始从事慈善工作，为一些无家可归的人提供食物，与其他人维持良好关系，试图去感觉内心的舒适及安全，但是一回家，当她面对自己，却看到内心深处什么也没有。她再一次陷入了黑暗。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">直到有人提议她去印度旅行，一切才开始真正发生改变。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/58756200_1517533968.com/mmbiz_jpg/w2ktexcvd9ok8eiabpkvt8jhjdnfab2icicjciw9nicttuib5gveptqebdcibg4po1elsiat4gxjsibicbudy26kvsnqmg/0" width="100%" height="auto" title="" alt="" style="padding: 10px; z-index: -1; cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid rgb(220, 220, 221); border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 6px; width: 635px;"/></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/65798300_1517533968.png" alt="图片-公众号-序号5.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0em; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70); font-size: 15px;"><strong>从印度静心中心到全球</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70); font-size: 15px;"><strong>她想要让更多人找到幸福</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">29岁那年，奥南朵第一次前往印度，原本只打算停留2周就回去，结果没想到，一待就是30年。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70);"><strong><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">在印度普纳的国际静心中心，她发现了一个全新的自己</span></strong></span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">，开始了解到她之前的生命完全生活在无意识之中。就像一个机器人，只是在社会系统中做事情，却从没有想过为自己做点什么。她总是担心别人会怎样想她，怎样批判她，总是生活在恐惧与紧张之中。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">为了改变这一切，她开始踏上寻找自己、寻找幸福的旅程。而她的方法就是：静心、冥想与不断地觉察。最终，她成功了，生命中所有的热爱、喜悦都开始如影随形。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">30年一场蜕变，历经一生精彩的淬炼，<span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);"><strong>她圆融成熟的生命最终饱含着喜乐、热情与智慧。</strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">之后，为了帮助更多人找到幸福，奥南朵开始在世界各地开设线下课程，带领更多人走入冥想，向内探寻幸福。</span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/71747500_1517533968.com/mmbiz_jpg/kf10ne2xwqniicd6gqtsuiniawl2gayicst9iblhrizwffnqcdlawb07cyq2ioxevwhxpfsxgibibirqvyrqqsuq4qfq/640" width="100%" height="auto" title="" alt="" style="white-space: normal; border: 1px solid rgb(220, 220, 221); border-radius: 0px; padding: 10px; box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 6px;"/></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">她说：<span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);"><strong><span style="max-width: 100%;">“<span style="max-width: 100%;">外在的享乐都是暂时的</span></span>，</strong></span><strong>过一阵子我们又要去寻找新的刺激。而内在的幸福不同，它是从内心深处泉涌而出的，来自一份和平，一份对自己的满意。能够感激自己、感激生命、感激一切，它就永远存在。”</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;">很多人都觉得冥想就要在寺庙里安静地坐着，或者到喜马拉雅山上去才有效，在如今这个快节奏的时代已经不适用了，但是奥南朵却认为，冥想是可以实践在生活中的。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);"><strong>因为冥想的重点就是觉知，就是更加有意识地看见自己是如何生活。</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">所有的紧张与压力都来自于过去和未来，而所谓的问题就是一种害怕将来会发生什么。</span></p><p style="margin: 0em 1em 15px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif&#39;&#39;; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">如果我们能活在当下，只是看到眼前的情景，就去处理眼前的情况，那么就会变得放松快乐，幸福和喜悦也会油然而生。</span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxgEthLVh1357/image/ueditor/79386000_1517533968.com/mmbiz_jpg/bzhkkhh4npzicmqhuodojwkdiapabjcxib3eyxrjhzhxqay9pujdibldkfakkzncs3fmvich3fygpjf0tpy889vvlxw/640" width="100%" height="auto" title="" alt="" style="white-s